  "text": "Primary productivity over the Mackenzie Delta/Beaufort Shelf is about 3.3 × 10 6 tons yr −1 of particulate organic carbon during late spring and summer [CITATION_1] . Production by ice algae accounts for less than 10 % of the marine production in this area [CITATION_2] .",
